Text:
Sup all... I do not usualy plug CD's for people unless i like them... so have a 
look @ this... Peace... 

"I've been working on these songs for a while, the first intent was to compile 
enough to make an album. Life happens and instead I decided to release it as 
a mix-tape. There are a few songs already on the internet anyway, so I figure 
I'd just release the full thing. Hope y'all enjoy the music"...

For Promotional Use Only... Remember to support the artists...
Anyway enjoy the Music,it is free!!!!
